pdf_document = fitz.open('/workspace/i-9.pdf')

# Define the field values with modified DOB
field_values = {
    'Last Name (Family Name)': 'Sharma',
    'First Name Given Name': 'Priya',
    'Employee Middle Initial (if any)': '',
    'Employee Other Last Names Used (if any)': '',
    'Address Street Number and Name': '348 Robert Rue',
    'Apt Number (if any)': '',
    'City or Town': 'Jenkinschester',
    'State': 'DE',
    'ZIP Code': '68188',

    'Employees E-mail Address': 'lorithompson@peters-young.net',
    'Telephone Number': '647.650.3357',
    'Foreign Passport Number and Country of IssuanceRow1': 'UDC0FYRIW, Bulgaria',
    'Exp Date mmddyyyy': '11/28/2025',
    'Signature of Employee': 'Priya Sharma',
    "Today's Date mmddyyy": '11/14/2024'
}

# Fill the form fields
filled_count = 0
for widget in page.widgets():
    field_name = widget.field_name
    if field_name in field_values:
        value = field_values[field_name]
        widget.field_value = value
        widget.update()
        filled_count += 1
        print(f"Filled: {field_name} = {value}")

        widget.update()
        filled_count += 1
        print(f"Checked: CB_4 (A noncitizen authorized to work)")
        break

print(f"\nTotal fields filled: {filled_count}")

# Save the filled PDF

pdf_document.close()

print(f"\nPDF saved to: {output_path}")
